  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "`WithUser` and `WithUID` options are needed to run container as a specific user.\r\n\r\n`WithUID` is simple, it's fine to leave users to do it themselves.\r\nHowever, `WithUser` is a bit hard, it needs to mount container rootfs first, read `/etc/passwd` etc., which seems better to implement in containerd.",
